The core functionality of Meta V2

See ../../README.md for details, reminders, bugs, todos, etc.

################################################################################
FILE LISTING:

README:
  Documents each file in the directory.

Makefile:
  Various targets related to this directory.

.gitignore:
  Files to ignore in the git repo.

?.meta/
  Repository of files written by the meta compiler.

parser.meta:
  The Meta V2 parsing code.

root.meta2:
  An implementation of the metax.root namespace in Meta. 

test.meta2:
  An implementation of the metax.test namespace in Meta.

testdata/
  Testdata for the Meta compiler code base.
